WEBVTT

00:01.626 --> 00:03.284
Where there are
now two land masses,

00:03.309 --> 00:04.628
there once was just one.

00:04.629 --> 00:06.996
The Book of Leaves
has to be here.

00:07.064 --> 00:08.232
Take whatever steps are
necessary

00:08.300 --> 00:10.802
to find our spy.
Do it quickly.

00:10.870 --> 00:13.206
It is God's will
to break Lorenzo

00:13.274 --> 00:14.775
and all who support him.

00:14.843 --> 00:16.879
With the exception of
DaVinci, I agree with you.

00:16.947 --> 00:19.615
Those weapons he makes,
they could all be ours.

00:19.683 --> 00:22.485
Rome has more men,
and the Lord, on its side.

00:22.553 --> 00:24.955
Well, we've got
ten pipe organ muskets

00:25.023 --> 00:28.393
capable of firing 33 rounds
a minute on ours.

00:28.460 --> 00:32.030
Ten guns. Good to know.
Thank you for that.

00:32.098 --> 00:33.498
Papers with the papal seal.

00:33.566 --> 00:35.935
A list of locations
to hide them.

00:36.003 --> 00:38.337
- Where did you find this?
- Signor Becchi's quarters.

00:38.405 --> 00:39.973
All along
the traitor was you.

00:40.040 --> 00:41.909
Lorenzo,
this is a mistake.

00:47.541 --> 00:51.541
